        <section name="Download">
            <p>A single Force Field X distribution supports Linux, Mac OS X and Microsoft Windows
            operating systems for both 32-Bit and 64-Bit hardware.
            </p>
            <p>The distribution includes:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Launcher for the command line compiler</li>
                <li>Examples</li>
                <li>Scripts</li>
            </ul>
            <p>System requirement:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>A Java Runtime Environment (JRE) version 1.6.0 or later</li>
            </ul>
